casebody.data: The People of the State of New York ex rel. John A. Sadowy, Appellant, against J. Vernel Jackson, as Warden of Clinton State Prison, Respondent. Submitted February 21, 1949; decided March 3, 1949. John A. Sadowy, appellant in person. Nathaniel L. Goldstein, Attorney-General {Wendell P. Brown, Herman N. Harcourt and George A. Bads of,counsel), for respondent.
